replies.author: 隔壁柴先生
replies.txt_content:
同一楼，将authme的MySQL关闭切换为本地数据库
打开authme插件文件夹打开config找到下面内容
DataSource:
    # What type of database do you want to use?
    # Valid values: sqlite, mysql
    backend: 'mysql'
将改为sqlite即可
